          "Hadith.3043 - It is narrated from Suwayd al-Qallāʾ, from Muhammad ibn Muslim, from Imam Abu Jaʿfar (as), who said:\n\"The sacrifice (udhiyya) is obligatory upon anyone who can afford it, whether young or old, and it is also a sunnah.\""
